  "label": "Cinderstep Sleeping Cell",
  "description": "Cinderstep Sleeping Cell is a narrow, pressure-rated bedroom partitioned from the habitation bay by a gasketed bulkhead and sound-damped panels. Twin recessed bunks are set into ferrocrete niches, their edges armored with void-black adamantine ribs that continue the quarter’s blast-bracing pattern. A stenciled inventory band and quarantine placards run along the headwall above a sealed footlocker recess, reducing the space to regulated storage and rest. Lumen strips behind armored grilles cast hard white light that flattens every surface and leaves no corner unlit.",
